ate-900/70 p-6\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold\">Sponsored resource pages</h2><p class=\"mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-400\">Support useful educational content with a clearly disclosed, contextually relevant placement.</p></section><section class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold\">Newsletter sponsorship</h2><p class=\"mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-400\">Introduce a useful product to subscribers interested in new converters and productivity tools.</p></section></div><div class=\"mt-12 rounded-2xl border border-blue-400/20 bg-blue-400/5 p-7\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-black\">Discuss a placement</h2><p class=\"mt-3 text-slate-300\">Email<!-- --> <a class=\"font-semibold text-blue-300\" href=\"mailto:partners@a2zconvertor.co.uk\">partners@a2zconvertor.co.uk</a> <!-- -->with your product, audience fit and preferred placement.</p><a class=\"mt-5 inline-flex text-sm font-semibold text-blue-300\" href=\"/partners\">View partnership options</a></div></div></section><footer class=\"border-t border-white/10 px-6 py-16\"><div class=\"mx-auto mb-12 max-w-7xl\"><section class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-5\"><div class=\"\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-black\">Get new free tools and productivity tips.</h2><p class=\"mt-3 max-w-2xl leading-7 text-slate-400\">Be first to know when we launch new converters, PDF tools and browser-based productivity tools.</p><form class=\"mt-5 flex gap-3 flex-col\"><label class=\"sr-only\" for=\"_R_tbsnlb_\">Email address</label><input id=\"_R_tbsnlb_\" type=\"email\" required=\"\" autoComplete=\"email\" placeholder=\"you@example.com\" class=\"min-w-0 flex-1 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-950 px-4 py-3 text-white outline-none focus:border-blue-500\" name=\"email\" value=\"\"/><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"source\" value=\"a2zconvertor\"/><button type=\"submit\" class=\"rounded-xl bg-blue-600 px-5 py-3 font-semibold text-white hover:bg-blue-500\">Join by email</button><